social_posts.post_text: Good to kick things off on two wheels

A few of my favorites from a recent rebrand project with @fort_west @southerndistilling . Huge thanks to @robb_blah_blah for the creative director skills and grinding it out for several days in the southern heat (he’s from PNW). There were only a few casualties…Rob dropped his camera in the river, I smashed a strobe into the concrete, and tore my transmitter off my hot shoe. I’ve learned that comes with the territory and all a part of the process of making projects like this a success.
Excited to share some of the work my amazing team and I spent much of last year working on for the Free Fly Sp23 release. To kick things off, here’s a few from our tarpon trip in the keys.

So we asked our friend and northern Oregon native, @Jarettjuarez, to show us the ropes, giving us a local’s look at the best spots around town.
